100001.name: Universal Enhanced Rigging (Experimental) +α
100001.desc: Buli? Did I just get an upgrade buli? Now, I can fight too buli!

101020.desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Dewey, Hull Number DD-349.

101021.name: Summer Longing
101021.desc: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?

101022.name: A Christmas Thank-You
101022.desc: Lexington gave me this Christmas costume as a thank-you for always supporting her. Commander, do you think I look... pretty in it?

101030.name: Cassin
101030.desc: Mahan-class destroyer - Cassin, Hull Number DD-372!

101031.name: Shopping Carte Blanche
101031.desc: I know I said we'd go shopping after school, but walking is so exhausting... I'll just hitch a ride in this cart. Looks sturdy enough...

101039.name: Cassin (Retrofit)
101039.desc: Commander... I think I've been in the house too long. My body feels different... Oh? I've improved? I see... Wonderful! I guess I can keep staying inside...

101040.name: Downes
101040.desc: Mahan-class destroyer - Downes, Hull Number DD-375!

101041.name: Part-Time Bomber
101041.desc: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪

101049.name: Downes (Retrofit)
101049.desc: Rawr! I'm Tiger Downes! What do you think, Commander? I feel great now! Faster. Stronger! Let's head out to sea and cause some trouble!

101050.name: Gridley
101050.desc: Gridley-class destroyer - Gridley, Hull Number DD-380!

101051.name: Christmas Photoshoot
101051.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?

101060.name: Craven
101060.desc: Gridley-class destroyer - Craven, Hull Number DD-382!

101061.name: Cheerleader On The Playground
101061.desc: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.

101070.name: McCall
101070.desc: Gridley-class destroyer - McCall, Hull Number DD-400!

101080.name: Maury
101080.desc: Gridley-class destroyer, Maury, Hull Number DD-401\n<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>

101090.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Fletcher, Hull Number DD-445!

101110.name: Charles Ausburne
101110.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!

101119.name: Charles Ausburne (Retrofit)
101119.desc: Captain Ausburne of the Little Beavers, upgraded and ready to go! Heh heh, my new-and-improved justice isn't just for show! Evildoers are gonna be in for a bad time!

101120.name: Thatcher
101120.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Thatcher, Hull Number DD-514!

101130.name: Aulick
101130.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Aulick, Hull Number DD-569!

101140.name: Foote
101140.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!

101150.name: Spence
101150.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Spence, Hull Number DD-512!

101160.name: Benson
101160.desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Benson, Hull Number DD-421!

101161.name: Cutie Pumpkin Pie
101161.desc: Fighting for love and peace this Halloween night, it's none other than the pumpkin-style Planet Bunny cutie pie, Benson!

101170.name: Laffey
101170.desc: Benson-class destroyer - Laffey, Hull Number DD-459!

101172.name: Snow Rabbit and Candy Apple
101172.desc: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?

101173.name: White Rabbit Welcomes the Spring
101173.desc: Have a happy and auspicious New Year? Uh.... can I go now...? I'm feeling a bit sleepy, so can I go back to sleep?

101174.name: Bunny Clerk?
101174.desc: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you “valued guest?” Um... I don’t really get it...

101175.name: Picnic Adventure?
101175.desc: Commander, ahhn... Umm, Commander, Laffey does not need to be fed... Rather, Laffey should be the one feeding you...

101176.name: Bunny Idol @Unmotivated
101176.desc: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?

101177.name: Sleep to Clean Another Day
101177.desc: Yaaawn... Laffey's cleaning her room, Commander... If you don't wanna help then just find a place to sit... Anyway, back to cleaning... Zzz...

101178.name: White Rabbit's Oath
101178.desc: Laffey seems to have changed a bit... Commander, do you like how Laffey is now?

101179.name: Laffey (Retrofit)
101179.desc: Laffey, improved and reporting in! I feel energized and ready to redouble my efforts! Hey, Commander, I still don't want you to touch my ears...

101240.name: Sims
101240.desc: Sims-class destroyer - Sims, Hull Number DD-409!

101249.name: Sims (Retrofit)
101249.desc: Y'know, Commander~ No matter how nice you are to me, I'm still going to prank you~ Oh, but if you want my help with pranking others, I'll consider it~ Heehee~

101250.name: Hammann
101250.desc: Sims-class Destroyer - Hammann, Hull Number DD-412!

101251.name: Rebellious Summer
101251.desc: I'm not really happy at all! But since you're bonding with me for once, I have to say... thank y... H-hmph! I didn't say anything!

101252.name: Prideful Fairy of the Ballroom
101252.desc: Hmph! I'm only here because you pleaded so desperately for me to come! Don't get any funny ideas! ...Why did I take so long to pick out my clothes? It... it's not like I was trying to impress anyone! I definitely wasn't looking forward to this party or anything!

101253.name: Hammanyan Pawnch!
101253.desc: Ughh... These gloves are so heavy and the dress is too revealing. Why on earth did I decide to put these on... I can't show myself to Yorktown like this!

101254.name: Holy Night Surprise!
101254.desc: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!

101259.name: Hammann (Retrofit)
101259.desc: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!

101260.name: Eldridge
101260.desc: Cannon-class Destroyer Escort - Eldridge, Hull Number DE-173!

101261.name: Holy Night's Embrace
101261.desc: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?

101262.name: The Inquisitive Recluse
101262.desc: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...

101263.name: New Year's Outing
101263.desc: Commander... Sakura Empire's New Year, looks very fun, let's go together...? (Eldridge looks at you expectantly)

101264.name: Kitty Idol
101264.desc: Eldridge and kitties, idol mode... Commander, you like...?

101265.name: Moon Festival Spacewalk
101265.desc: Eldridge, arriving at designated altitude... Moon, mooncake, and Manjuus spotted...

101270.name: Bailey
101270.desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!

101271.name: Trickster Black Rabbit
101271.desc: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!

101272.name: Jolly Saint Bunnylass!
101272.desc: Your Bunny Santa has arrived! That's right – not regular ol' Santa, but Bunny Santa! The real Santa's busy, so Bailey from Planet Bunny is here to help out!

101279.name: Bailey (Retrofit)
101279.desc: The day has finally arrived~! Bunnies, are you ready? Bailey's debut show is about to begin! Commander, sisters, come and see my bunny magic!

101290.name: Radford
101290.desc: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Radford, Hull Number DD-446!

101291.name: Sweet Magic!
101291.desc: Commander, the sweet magic within my tome lets me turn things into candy! Hehe, that sounds pretty convincing— ...Eh, Commander? Wh-when'd you get here?!

101300.name: Jenkins
101300.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!

101301.name: Light of the Holiest Star
101301.desc: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?

101310.name: Nicholas
101310.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!

101311.name: Nurse Nicholas
101311.desc: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.

101312.name: Surprise!?
101312.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander. I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... zzz...

101313.name: Summer Cleaning "Volunteer"
101313.desc: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~

101314.name: After-School Promise
101314.desc: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...

101319.name: Nicholas (Retrofit)
101319.desc: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...

101330.name: Bush
101330.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bush, Hull Number DD-529.

101331.name: Budding Painter
101331.desc: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!

101340.name: Hazelwood
101340.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.

101350.name: Bache
101350.desc: Yoohoo~! You the Commander? You look kinda weaksauce, though~! Name's Bache! I'm joining this fleet, starting today! I'll take good care of you, so just kick back and get ready for my greatness!

101351.name: Gorgeous Speed-star
101351.desc: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!

101352.name: Showy Sports Star
101352.desc: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!

101360.name: Hobby
101360.desc: Benson class Destroyer— Hobby, hull number DD-610.

101361.name: Little Idol Schoolgirl
101361.desc: Here comes the debut of school uniform Hobby~ Commander, how do I look? Hobby is all grown up~

101370.name: Kalk
101370.desc: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.

101371.name: Snow Fairy Schoolgirl
101371.desc: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?

101382.name: Style of the East
101382.desc: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?

101392.name: Eastern Etiquette
101392.desc: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?

101400.name: Aylwin
101400.desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.

101401.name: Sunday Aquarium Visit
101401.desc: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~

101410.name: Stanly
101410.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Stanly , Hull Number DD-478.

101420.name: Smalley
101420.desc: Destroyer Smalley, reporting in. Interests: kickboxing.

101421.name: Candy Courier
101421.desc: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.

101430.name: Halsey Powell
101430.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Halsey Powell, Hull Number DD-686.

101431.name: Spring's Lucky Star
101431.desc: Halsey Powell is making her debut as your lucky star for the Spring Festival! Commander, if you show me a fun time, you'll be blessed with good luck this year!

101440.name: Cooper
101440.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.

101441.name: Blazing Tennis Battle
101441.desc: 30 to 15... Next match will be mine, you hear! Oh, Commander, are you here to play a round of tennis?

101442.name: Heartwarming Holiday Hearth
101442.desc: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!

101450.name: Allen M. Sumner
101450.desc: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?

101451.name: Charming Rabbit
101451.desc: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!

101460.name: Stephen Potter
101460.desc: Fletcher-class Stephen Potter here. You've probably met a million of my sisters already, so I'll spare you my life story. See you around.

101461.name: Chillaxation Station
101461.desc: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.

101470.name: Morrison
101470.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Morrison, Hull Number DD-560.

101471.name: Sleeping Bunny
101471.desc: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?

101480.name: Ingraham
101480.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Ingraham, Hull Number DD-694.

101481.name: Fixin' for a Mixin'
101481.desc: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!

101490.name: Bristol
101490.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Bristol, Hull Number DD-857.

101491.name: Tales from the Empery
101491.desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! The time's finally come to look into the age-old legends from the Dragon Empery! The truth behind these legends is bound to be as fascinating as the legends themselves!

101500.name: Hammann II
101500.desc: Edsall-class destroyer escort – Hammann II, Hull Number DE-131.

101501.name: Another Rebellious Summer
101501.desc: Hmph! I only promised to come to the beach because I was worried you'd be lonely! There's no deeper meaning—w-wait! What are you doing?! Stooop!

102010.name: Omaha
102010.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Omaha, Hull Number CL-4!

102020.name: Raleigh
102020.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Raleigh, Hull Number CL-7!

102030.name: Brooklyn
102030.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!

102040.name: Phoenix
102040.desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Phoenix, Hull Number CL-46!

102050.name: Helena
102050.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!

102051.name: New Year's Bluebird
102051.desc: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.

102052.name: May I Have this Dance?
102052.desc: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...

102058.name: Miracle in White
102058.desc: Wh-what do you think, Commander? Does it suit me? ...I never could've imagined getting to wear this even in my dreams, let alone experience the bliss I feel now... Thank you so, so much.

102059.name: Helena (Retrofit)
102059.desc: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!

102060.name: Atlanta
102060.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!

102070.name: Juneau
102070.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!

102071.name: In the Swan Garden
102071.desc: This swan is so soft and pettable... Heehee, it even let me put a ribbon on it. Now we have matching looks... Huh? You could take a picture of us? I-if it's not too much work then please, by all means!

102079.name: Juneau (Retrofit)
102079.desc: After all that painstaking work, I've f-finally managed to complete my retrofit! Even though I'm still afraid of getting hurt, I'll try to be brave for you, Commander!

102080.name: San Diego
102080.desc: Atlanta-class Light Cruiser – San Diego, Hull Number CL-53!

102081.name: Sandy Claus
102081.desc: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?

102088.name: No. 1 June Bride!
102088.desc: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!

102089.name: San Diego (Retrofit)
102089.desc: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?

102090.name: Cleveland
102090.desc: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!

102091.name: Reaper Fever
102091.desc: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?

102092.name: Gentry Knight
102092.desc: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!

102093.name: Road Trip!
102093.desc: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!

102094.name: New Year's Challenge!
102094.desc: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.

102095.name: Southbound Journey
102095.desc: Isn't it real exciting visiting a place you don't normally get to go? We don't often get opportunities to travel like this, so let's go look for delicious food and spectacular scenery!

102098.name: Heartfelt Moment
102098.desc: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?

102100.name: Columbia
102100.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.

102101.name: After-School Odette
102101.desc: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some Prince Charming, and it's super embarrassing.

102102.name: Across the Vast Prairies
102102.desc: ...Mm, that's good enough for today's journal entry. Wonder what Cleve's gonna think after reading this~ What do you think, Commander? Wait... Commander? Jeez, don't wander off when I'm all focused on my writing...

102120.name: Honolulu
102120.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!

102121.name: Umbrella Girl
102121.desc: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...

102122.name: Summer Accident?!
102122.desc: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!

102123.name: Manjuu Mischief
102123.desc: Just where did St. Louis find something like this... such shameless undergarments, if someone found out... Awawawaa! Commander, what are you doing in here? Get out right now!

102124.name: Among the Stalls
102124.desc: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!

102130.name: St. Louis
102130.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!

102131.name: Blue and White Pottery
102131.desc: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?

102132.name: Spirits in the Snow
102132.desc: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.

102133.name: Luxurious Wheels
102133.desc: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~

102140.name: Montpelier
102140.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.

102141.name: Flower of the Snowy Night
102141.desc: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.

102142.name: Persephone's Throne
102142.desc: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.

102160.name: Memphis
102160.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-13.

102161.name: Casual Vacation
102161.desc: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?

102162.name: Mystical Night
102162.desc: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?

102163.name: A Breath of Fresh Air
102163.desc: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.

102180.name: Concord
102180.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser— Concord, hull number CL-10.

102181.name: Red Apple Candy
102181.desc: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~

102182.name: Sweet☆Christmas
102182.desc: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~

102220.name: San Juan
102220.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.

102221.name: The Longing Princess
102221.desc: All right, dress looking good. Now just to check my makeup... Need to be thorough, so I don't embarrass myself in front of– What?! C-Commander?!

102230.name: Birmingham
102230.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Birmingham, Hull Number CL-62.

102231.name: Rider of Red
102231.desc: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

102232.name: Fruitful Snow of an Auspicious Year
102232.desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.

102233.name: To Where the Wind Blows
102233.desc: The wind and the waves are great today. You wanna try windsurfing after this, Commander? It's a lot of fun and I can teach you the... Hang on, there's a good wind coming and I've got to catch it!

102240.name: Cleveland μ
102240.desc: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!

102250.name: Biloxi
102250.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Biloxi, Hull Number CL-80.

102251.name: Dapper Gangstress
102251.desc: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?

102252.name: Empress in the Silk Seat
102252.desc: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?

102253.name: Night Sky's Brilliant Blue Blossoms
102253.desc: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upo

102254.name: Romeo or Juliet?
102254.desc: The cast is all here. So, what do we rehearse first? The part where we elope and live happily ever after? Hahahah!

102260.name: Reno
102260.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Reno, Hull Number CL-96.

102261.name: Biggest Little Cheerleader
102261.desc: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!

102262.name: Summer Spin-off
102262.desc: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?

102263.name: Reno Bunnino
102263.desc: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?

102264.name: Spring's Inspiration
102264.desc: Check this out, Commander! Hehehe, I added a little firework launcher to my superhero gadgets. Cool, huh? ...Your interest lies more in my new look? But... the firework...

102270.name: Marblehead
102270.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Marblehead, Hull Number CL-12.

102271.name: Boxing Girl!
102271.desc: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~

102272.name: Charmer in the Snowy Reflection
102272.desc: Whoa! Talk about a stunning view! You like, totally know all the best spots in the city, Commander~ Hehe, okay, so... Merry Christmas!

102273.name: Moongazing on the 29½th
102273.desc: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡

102274.name: Not-So-Serendipitous Rain
102274.desc: Phew... Should be in the clear now. Oh, hey, Commander. Whatcha doing here? Waiting for a cutie to show up or something? Surely it can't be a coincidence... right?

102290.name: Boise
102290.desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Boise, Hull Number CL-47.

102291.name: Sheepish Sapphire
102291.desc: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...

102292.name: Castle Tales
102292.desc: Um, I decided to try on a costume, since it's Halloween and all... Do you think I got that witchy look down...?

102293.name: Jade Mermaid
102293.desc: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...

103010.name: Pensacola
103010.desc: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Pensacola, Hull Number CA-24!

103020.name: Salt Lake City
103020.desc: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!

103030.name: Northampton
103030.desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!

103040.name: Chicago
103040.desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Chicago, Hull Number CA-29!

103050.name: Houston
103050.desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Houston, Hull Number CA-30!

103060.name: Portland
103060.desc: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Portland, Hull Number CA-33!

103061.name: At School With Indy!
103061.desc: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!

103069.name: Portland (Retrofit)
103069.desc: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...

103070.name: Indianapolis
103070.desc: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Indianapolis, Hull Number CA-35!

103071.name: At School With My Sister...
103071.desc: School life... It's nice as long as you and my sister are here... I think...

103072.name: The Light of Circle City
103072.desc: Oh. Good evening, Commander. Do you want some steak? It goes great with wine.

103080.name: Astoria
103080.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Astoria, hull number CA-34.

103081.name: Pure "Gurl?"
103081.desc: Huh? Commander? ... Wait, why are you staring at me like I'm some exotic animal? C-cute? Ehehe... Th-thanks...

103082.name: Black Bunny Carnival
103082.desc: Heyyo! You ready for this, Commander? It's carnival day! You can have all the drinks you want, it's on the house!

103090.name: Quincy
103090.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Quincy, hull number CA-39.

103091.name: Sizzling Summer, Brisk Breeze
103091.desc: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?

103100.name: Vincennes
103100.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Vincennes, hull number CA-44.

103102.name: Leisurely ABC's
103102.desc: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~

103110.name: Wichita
103110.desc: Wichita-class heavy cruiser – Wichita, Hull Number CA-45! \n<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>

103111.name: The General's Banquet
103111.desc: It's about time you showed up, Commander. Now, show me some spirit! As my lieutenant, don't do anything slovenly that would incur the mockery of others! Very well, let's move out!

103112.name: Domineering Witchita
103112.desc: Tonight I am not a renowned naval general, I am a feared commander of witches! And you... Yes, you're not my lieutenant, you are my arcane familiar!

103121.name: Evening Agricole
103121.desc: To your prestige, and to your continued victories, Commander. Hehe, I do find myself in the mood for rum tonight. Care to keep me company for a while?

103130.name: Minneapolis
103130.desc: New Orleans class Heavy Cruiser— Minneapolis, hull number CA-36.

103131.name: Wild Huntress Schoolgirl
103131.desc: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?

103132.name: eXtreme Games
103132.desc: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!

103133.name: Holy Night Ride
103133.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! Right now, I'm Santa Claus! And this guy over here is my partner in delivering presents! Right, this is a present for you. C'mon, go ahead and take it!

103138.name: Trapper White
103138.desc: Commander, why's that Quincy so happy to see me in this outfit? It's hard to move around in, and there's all this stuff flapping around that makes it hard to hunt. What do you think of this outfit?

103140.name: San Francisco
103140.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – San Francisco, Hull Number CA-38.

103141.name: Funny Bunny!
103141.desc: Music! Lights! Refreshments! We're all set! Welcome to San Francisco's party! Come and enjoy yourself!

103142.name: It's Showtime!
103142.desc: Good evening, Puddin'! Welcome to my pole dancing show! You aren't going home tonight 'til you're head over heels for me♪

103160.name: Baltimore
103160.desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Baltimore, Hull Number CA-68.

103161.name: After-School Ace
103161.desc: Oh, you wanna observe my club activities, Commander? Ahah, as you can tell, it's just a sports club with the goal of making you sweat. Nothing suspicious about that, is there...?

103162.name: Black Ace
103162.desc: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!

103163.name: Evening Breeze Minuet
103163.desc: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?

103164.name: Ace's Travel Journal
103164.desc: "Our meeting here must have been preordained by fate. Hail to you. I am a passing traveler by the name of Baltimore." ...Hahah, it's nothing. Just some lines I came up with to match my traditional getup. Did they do the trick, Commander?

103165.name: Finish Line Flagbearer
103165.desc: Heya, Commander. You here to spectate the race? Strap in, 'cause it's gonna be wild... My getup? They asked me to help out the grid girls, so yeah. Just hope I'll do a good job of building hype for the race.

103240.name: Bremerton
103240.desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Bremerton, Hull Number CA-130.

103241.name: Scorching-Hot Training
103241.desc: *pant*... *pant*... Man, it's so sunny today... Commander, or should I say, "Coach," could ya lend me your parasol? I'm starting to feel my brains melting away...

103242.name: Kung Fu Cruiser
103242.desc: "Stop right there, evildoers! You've managed to evade justice all this time, but the hour of judgment is finally upon you!" ...Hmm, making the perfect flashy debut is pretty tough, isn't it?

103243.name: Day-Off Date
103243.desc: I reckon we've done enough shopping for the moment. Let's stop and chill here for a bit, then have another look around~♪

103244.name: Relaxation Consultation
103244.desc: Welcome to Bremerton's counseling corner! Actually, I came up with this idea just for you, since you're always working so hard... Tadaaah~! I've prepared us some matching sleepwear~♪

103250.name: Baltimore μ
103250.desc: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.

103260.name: Northampton II
103260.desc: Oregon City-class heavy cruiser – Northampton II, Hull Number CA-125.

103261.name: Swimming Star
103261.desc: Whew. How many laps have I done since my last break...? Oh. Commander, are you here to hone your swimming skills too?

105010.name: Nevada
105010.desc: Nevada-class battleship – Nevada, Hull Number BB-36!

105011.name: A Magnificent Banquet
105011.desc: Howdy, young'un! Aren't you tired from goin' around greetin' fancy people? Come over here and relax with me and some good food.

105019.name: Nevada (Retrofit)
105019.desc: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!

105020.name: Oklahoma
105020.desc: Nevada-class battleship – Oklahoma, Hull Number BB-37!

105021.name: Piratey Transformation!
105021.desc: Howdy, Commander! Oh, this outfit? I've been super into this kind of stuff lately! I even added some jack-o-lanterns for extra ambiance and had some Manjuus help out. So what's the verdict? Pretty cool, isn't it?

105029.name: Oklahoma (Retrofit)
105029.desc: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!

105030.name: Pennsylvania
105030.desc: Pennsylvania-class battleship – Pennsylvania, Hull Number BB-38!

105031.name: The Keystone General
105031.desc: Halt! Who are you?! ...Oh, it's you, Commander. I briefly mistook you for a spy there. Why are you here? To spectate? Or, God forbid, to gather intel on my army?

105040.name: Arizona
105040.desc: Pennsylvania-class Battleship – Arizona, Hull Number BB-39!

105041.name: Enchantress from Afar
105041.desc: I heard these clothes are from the Dragon Empery, but they're a bit... Umm, it's not that I dislike them, but the thought of you seeing me in them is rather embarrassing... B-but it's not like I'm going to start crying...

105070.name: Tennessee
105070.desc: Tennessee-class battleship – Tennessee, Hull Number BB-43!

105080.name: California
105080.desc: Tennessee-class battleship – California, Hull Number BB-44!

105090.name: Colorado
105090.desc: Colorado class battleship— Colorado, hull number BB-45

105092.name: Traveling Melody
105092.desc: Hmm-hum-hum... So very cute~♪ ...Commander? Um, about that... Please do me a favor and forget you heard anything.

105100.name: Maryland
105100.desc: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46

105110.name: West Virginia
105110.desc: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.

105120.name: North Carolina
105120.desc: North Carolina class battleship, North Carolina. Hull Number BB-55.

105121.name: The Heart's Desire
105121.desc: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?

105130.name: Washington
105130.desc: North Carolina class battleship, Washington. Hull Number BB-56.

105131.name: Jubilant Smile
105131.desc: Sup, Commander? ...Looking good? I don't think this outfit's anything special... You better not be trying to cozy up to me, or I'll knock your teeth out!

105140.name: South Dakota
105140.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!

105141.name: Solo Concert
105141.desc: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.

105170.name: New Jersey
105170.desc: Iowa-class battleship – New Jersey, Hull Number BB-62.

105171.name: Exhilarating Steps!
105171.desc: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?

105178.name: Snow-White Ceremony
105178.desc: The indomitable Black Dragon... I mean, the adorable New Jersey makes her bridal appearance! Hehe~ Stunned, arent'cha? Of course you are, honey~♪ How wouldn't you be?

105190.name: Massachusetts
105190.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.

105191.name: Dressed to Impress
105191.desc: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...

105200.name: Alabama
105200.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Alabama, Hull Number BB-60.

105201.name: Untarnished Silver, Silken Gold
105201.desc: Hrmm... Lotta orders to work through... Runnin' a Dragon Empery restaurant ain't easy. Hmm? You here for some chow too, Commander? Then how about... I put you ahead in line?

106010.name: Long Island
106010.desc: Long Island-class escort carrier – Long Island, Hull Number CVE-1!

106011.name: Long Island - Indoor Slacker
106011.desc: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...

106013.name: Long Island's Spooky Stream
106013.desc: "Tune in everyone, Gamer Girl L.I. is about to begin her spooky Halloween special stream~" ...Well, that should do it for my channel intro... Hmm, wonder how many viewers I'll get~

106019.name: Long Island (Retrofit)
106019.desc: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!

106020.name: Bogue
106020.desc: Bogue-class escort carrier — Bogue, Hull Number CVE-9!

106029.name: Bogue (Retrofit)
106029.desc: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...

106550.name: Casablanca
106550.desc: Casablanca-class escort carrier – Casablanca, Hull Number CVE-55.

106551.name: Cheer Squad on Break
106551.desc: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?

107010.name: Langley
107010.desc: Langley-class aicraft carrier ー Langley, Hull Number CV-1!

107019.name: Langley (Retrofit)
107019.desc: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!

107020.name: Lexington
107020.desc: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Lexington, Hull Number CV-2!

107021.name: The Beauty of Spring
107021.desc: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~

107030.name: Saratoga
107030.desc: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Saratoga, Hull Number CV-3!

107031.name: Seven Seas of Rest
107031.desc: Even if we don't get to relax on holiday, it's always good to have a swimsuit! Ok, let's go! Are you ready to swim?

107032.name: Hibiscus-scented Idol
107032.desc: Hey everyone~! This time, Sister Sara has brought you fashion from a faraway land! Commander, what do you think of it?

107033.name: Virtual Idol
107033.desc: HAI DOMO~! I’m the virtual idol, Saratoga! Well, Commander, what do you think? I asked Kizuna AI to make this dress specifically for me, modeled after her outfit!

107034.name: Superstar of the Blue Seas
107034.desc: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!

107035.name: Silent Night Songstress
107035.desc: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?

107036.name: Spring's Opening Act!
107036.desc: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!

107037.name: The Sweetest Picnic!
107037.desc: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪

107038.name: Ring the Bell of Joy
107038.desc: You ready, Commander? ...Come on, don't give me a "just one moment" right before the finish line~ It's time to imprint my adorable dress into your memory forever~♡

107039.name: Saratoga (Retrofit)
107039.desc: Sister Sara is leaving her nest and going in a new direction! I'm now making my official debut as Saratoga: The Little Witch Idol! I'm leaving my PR to you, Commander~

107040.name: Ranger
107040.desc: Ranger-class aircraft carrier ー Ranger, Hull Number CV-4!

107049.name: Ranger (Retrofit)
107049.desc: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!

107050.name: Yorktown
107050.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Yorktown, Hull Number CV-5!

107051.name: Evening I Can't Remember
107051.desc: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?

107052.name: Saintly Wings
107052.desc: Across seven steps, in a tower atop a hill, you'll find the king's resting place... Hehe. Will you come with me to Utopia, Commander? I'm joking, of course, but I am very glad we could make this journey together.

107060.name: Enterprise
107060.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!

107061.name: Reindeer Master
107061.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! I shall be Santa Claus tonight, so make sure to hang up your stockings on the fireplace before going to sleep!

107062.name: Blooming Peony
107062.desc: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.

107063.name: Anniversary Ride
107063.desc: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!

107064.name: Soaring Wings of Freedom
107064.desc: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!

107065.name: Heroic Finery
107065.desc: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.

107066.name: Wind Catcher
107066.desc: Commander, did you come to watch the race? You know... I'd rather be down there competing than standing around over here. That feeling of being able to seize the wind... Don't you think that racing and sailing share the same essence?

107067.name: Bon Voyage
107067.desc: It feels odd taking an extended leave just to go on vacation... but I guess you need breaks to stay on top of your game. With that in mind, let's make every minute count, Commander!

107068.name: Starlight Oath
107068.desc: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...

107070.name: Hornet
107070.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Hornet, Hull Number CV-8!

107071.name: Bubbly Anniversary!
107071.desc: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!

107072.name: Freshly-Baked Bonding!
107072.desc: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!

107073.name: Cheering Justice!
107073.desc: Let's keep it up, everyone! One more point, and we can make a comeback!!! ...Hah... *gulp gulp*... Whew~! Thanks a billion for the drink, Commander! And thanks for watching over us as well!

107080.name: Wasp
107080.desc: Wasp-class aircraft carrier, Wasp. Hull Number CV-7.

107090.name: Essex
107090.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.

107091.name: A Trip Down Route 66
107091.desc: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.

107092.name: Craft Fairytail
107092.desc: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!

107093.name: Brush and Ink
107093.desc: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!

107094.name: Detective Essex
107094.desc: My eagle has gone missing... Just as Enterprise said, there's something strange going on in this port–– Wait, I definitely smell a case in the making! Commander, let's get to the bottom of this together!

107100.name: Yorktown II
107100.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Yorktown II, Hull Number CV-10.

107101.name: Bright-Sky Mermaid
107101.desc: How does this look? ...Ah, it's nothing to worry about. Do you think I should adjust the string a bit...? Hmm... Eek!!! I'm so sorry, Commander... A-are you alright...?

107110.name: Intrepid
107110.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Intrepid, Hull Number CV-11.

107111.name: One Intrepid Pitch
107111.desc: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?

107120.name: Hornet II
107120.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Hornet II, Hull Number CV-12.

107121.name: Racing Across the Waves!
107121.desc: The title of fastest in the port is miiiine, hahaha! Commandeer, did you see how badass I was just now? There's a whole lot more I'd like to show you, but it'll hafta wait 'til the next race... Well, I'll let you ride with me later, so look forward to it~♪

107140.name: Ticonderoga
107140.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Ticonderoga, Hull Number CV-14.

107141.name: Show Stopper!
107141.desc: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!

107170.name: Bunker Hill
107170.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.

107171.name: Mission Relaxation
107171.desc: Mission complete. Next up, a new recommendation from Long Island... Oh, Commander? Come make yourself comfortable.

107220.name: Independence
107220.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.

107221.name: Transfer Student From Afar
107221.desc: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.

107222.name: The Independent Line
107222.desc: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...

107223.name: Liberty and Leisure
107223.desc: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...

107224.name: The Tailwind of Opportunity
107224.desc: Just need to feed it a coin, then operate the crane with the joystick... Oh! I got one! That was easier than I expected.

107229.name: Independence (Retrofit)
107229.desc: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.

107231.name: Seaside Training
107231.desc: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.

107232.name: Lolipop Paradise
107232.desc: You're finally here? ...Ah, well, I only just got here as well, so don't worry about it. Anyway, shall we get going?

107233.name: Gift-Wrapped Reindeer
107233.desc: I'm done changing... Is this supposed to be a "reindeer" costume? It feels a bit too risqué... Oh, Commander, since you're already here, come get your Christmas present.

107270.name: Langley II
107270.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Langley II, Hull Number CVL-27.

107271.name: On-the-Clock Vacation
107271.desc: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!

107290.name: Bataan
107290.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.

107291.name: Comfy Cotton Jammies
107291.desc: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...

107380.name: Shangri-La
107380.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.

107381.name: Utopia's Collector
107381.desc: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?

107382.name: Explorer of the Lost World
107382.desc: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.

107990.name: Little Enterprise
107990.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.

108020.name: Albacore
108020.desc: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.

108021.name: Beneath the Black Dress
108021.desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

108022.name: A Catty Surprise!
108022.desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

108030.name: Cavalla
108030.desc: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.

108031.name: Convenience Store Raid!
108031.desc: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!

108032.name: Colorful Ceremony
108032.desc: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!

108040.name: Bluegill
108040.desc: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.

108041.name: Up-And-Coming Infielder
108041.desc: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!

108050.name: Albacore μ
108050.desc: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~

108060.name: Archerfish
108060.desc: Balao-class submarine – Archerfish, Hull Number SS-311.

108061.name: Coquettish Bunny
108061.desc: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~

108062.name: The Devil Next Door
108062.desc: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~

108071.name: Afternoon Stretches
108071.desc: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?

112010.name: Vestal
112010.desc: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!

112011.name: Revigorating Hestia
112011.desc: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!

131170.name: Sleepy Teriyaki Twister
131170.desc: Welcome. Would you like to try a Teriyaki Twister? I could go for a nap right now inside a nice, warm tortilla... Probably.

131171.name: Sleepageddon
131171.desc: Zzzzz... Good night... Laffey, is leveling up... Huh? Commander? Where'd all the monsters go...?

137030.name: Cup Ramen Ambassador?
137030.desc: Set, okay! Outfit, okay! All righty, everything's perfect!! Today, Sister Sara is taking on a brand new role as a brand ambassador! How about a taste, Commander?

199011.name: Gorgeous Party
199011.desc: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!

199012.name: Christmas Party Prep!
199012.desc: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?

199013.name: Sunfish Spell!
199013.desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!

199021.name: South Town Pearl
199021.desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?

199022.name: Lanier Swan
199022.desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?

199023.name: Exalted Vibrance
199023.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!

201010.name: Amazon
201010.desc: A-class prototype destoryer ー Amazon, Hull Number D39!

201011.name: Little Orchestra
201011.desc: No ball is complete without its orchestra! Here, as the leader of the Royal Destroyers Philharmonic, I'll be sure to liven up the night! Now to begin... woaaah! I stepped on my mantle?!

201019.name: Amazon (Retrofit)
201019.desc: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!

201020.name: Acasta
201020.desc: A-class destroyer – Acasta, Hull Number H09.

201021.name: Fashionable Outing
201021.desc: Hm? Guess we're both about to head out... Don't stare at me like that... Even I go outdoors sometimes... Since we're both, uh, headed the same way... maybe we could... walk there together?

201022.name: Lights of the Lantern Festival
201022.desc: I heard you're supposed to hang lanterns up everywhere during the Spring Festival... so Ardent and I gave it a try! What do you think? Pretty cute, right? Um... I was talking about the lanterns...

201023.name: Monochromatic Marvel
201023.desc: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...

201029.name: Acasta (Retrofit)
201029.desc: Ardent told me I "gotta stop looking so tired" and I "gotta be more girly," so I did it while I was retrofitting... Do you recognise me, Commander? ... Umm, I'm Acasta, okay?

201030.name: Ardent
201030.desc: A-class destroyer – Ardent, Hull Number H41.

201031.name: Ardent Valentine
201031.desc: Ehehe~ What do you think, Commander? If you're just going to say "cute," I won't know if you're talking about my school uniform or the chocolate I made...

201032.name: Master Ardent?
201032.desc: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪

201039.name: Ardent (Retrofit)
201039.desc: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!

201060.name: Beagle
201060.desc: B-class destroyer ー Beagle, Hull Number H30!

201070.name: Bulldog
201070.desc: B-class destroyer ー Bulldog, Hull Number H91!

201080.name: Comet
201080.desc: C-class destroyer ー Comet, Hull Number H00!

201089.name: Comet (Retrofit)
201089.desc: Do ya reckon... I you think I've become more idol-like? Mhm! As a new idol, I'll show y'all... I'll show you how hard I work as a new idol!

201090.name: Crescent
201090.desc: C-class destroyer ー Crescent, Hull Number H48!

201099.name: Crescent (Retrofit)
201099.desc: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!

201100.name: Cygnet
201100.desc: C-class destroyer ー Cygnet, Hull Number H83!

201101.name: Sea Star on Shore
201101.desc: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?

201102.name: Holy Night's Hymn
201102.desc: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...

201103.name: Winter Date
201103.desc: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Commander, did I keep you waiting long? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get going, then~

201104.name: An Offer To Be Maid
201104.desc: M-Master... good evening... C-Commander, don't stare at me so intently... *Whimper*... Saratoga told me that this is part of marketing yourself as an idol...

201105.name: Royal Fanfare
201105.desc: C-Commander? Erm... They picked me to be a cheerleader for the Royal Navy team at the sports thing, so I'm practicin' my cheers... D-don't stare at me like that... I'm shy enough... Already...

201109.name: Cygnet (Retrofit)
201109.desc: This outfit is a little tight... Yes, really? I understand. I've got to work harder for the Royal Navy!

201110.name: Foxhound
201110.desc: F-class destroyer ー Foxhound, Hull Number H69!

201119.name: Foxhound (Retrofit)
201119.desc: I've grown so much that I can't jump like I used to... Commander, are you surprised by my post-retrofit appearance? *Giggle*

201120.name: Fortune
201120.desc: F-class destroyer ー Fortune, Hull Number H70!

201121.name: Seraphic Sunshine
201121.desc: The weather is so nice and sunny, I'm sure whatever I do today will be a success. May everyone else have a good day today as well... Awauh! Little manjuu, are you okay? I can't believe I tripped...

201129.name: Fortune (Retrofit)
201129.desc: Is this really going to help you, Commander? Ah? I doubt our destiny will change with this... Just kidding, Commander! Anything for you.

201140.name: Glowworm
201140.desc: G-class destroyer ー Glowworm, Hull Number H92!

201141.name: Jokey Adjudicator
201141.desc: Ahahaha! It is I, Glowworm, the impartial and absolute judge! Any wrongdoers will have me to answer to! Guilty verdicts will result in headbutts!

201210.name: Javelin
201210.desc: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!

201212.name: Beach Picnic!
201212.desc: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!

201213.name: Let's Become Waitresses!
201213.desc: Tada! We’re all wearing the same uniform! It’s super cute, isn’t it? Heehee, I’ll be wearing it the entire time I’m on duty, so make sure to visit!

201215.name: Operation: Pillow Fight!
201215.desc: Laffey, Z23, Ayanami, and Unicorn - are you girls ready? Ehehe~ I'm not planning to lose to any of you today~!

201216.name: Energetic Idol @120% Motivation!
201216.desc: "Hello, everyone~! I'm Javelin, the new idol who arrived from the Royal Navy! I hope that my songs will be able to bring a smile to everyone's faces, so please take good care of me!" Hehe, how was that for an introduction, Commander?

201217.name: A Legend is Born?!
201217.desc: *pant* *pant*... I finally got it! The legendary hero's... Ah, d-don't worry about it! This thing might look a bit weird, but my ATK stat has indeed gone up!

201218.name: Blissful Purity
201218.desc: Today, I must be the happiest girl in the world! Hehe~

201219.name: Javelin (Retrofit)
201219.desc: Heavy attack mode prepared, ready to use ultimate firepower! Check out the incredible glow on this new gun!

201220.name: Juno
201220.desc: J-class destroyer ー Juno, Hull Number F46!

201221.name: Fairly Flavourful Festival
201221.desc: I love the bustle of a Sakura festival! Commander, care to try some of Akashi's takoyaki? I've heard their taste is out of this world!

201230.name: Vampire
201230.desc: V-class destroyer ー Vampire, Hull Number D68!

201231.name: The Breath of Spring
201231.desc: What do you think of my new outfit? You love it? Or just like it? Haha, your answer is written right on your face. Next... wait, wait, wait! I haven't put my socks on yet!

201232.name: Little Devil in White
201232.desc: Commander, I am now a nurse, so thou hast no choice but to give me thy blood~! Hehe, just kidding~!

201233.name: Night Princess's Regalia
201233.desc: Commander, thou promised to go to the festival with me, right? If thou forgot, I shall have to give thee a nibble upon the neck, ehehe~

201234.name: Night Princess Idol
201234.desc: Feast thine eyes upon Vampire's idol attire... is it not exquisite? Heheh, now thy gaze shall be fixed upon my performance alone~♪

201238.name: Eloi's Blessing
201238.desc: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.

201240.name: Jupiter
201240.desc: J-class destroyer – Jupiter, Hull Number F85.

201241.name: Fanclub Sleepover
201241.desc: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?

201250.name: Jersey
201250.desc: J-class destroyer – Jersey, Hull Number F72!

201261.name: Escort Me Please!
201261.desc: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

201320.name: Eskimo
201320.desc: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!

201321.name: Parkaless Prankster
201321.desc: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!

201331.name: One-Week Medical Experience?
201331.desc: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...

201332.name: Nereid's Discovery
201332.desc: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

201333.name: At Your Service
201333.desc: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~

201341.name: Fluttering in the Fair Breeze
201341.desc: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?

201351.name: Fright-Night Scaredy-Cat
201351.desc: D-don't worry, Janus... There's no such thing as Halloween ghouls... Hyeep?! A c-cat?! *whimper*... Jervis, Commander, please come save me...!

201352.name: Fear of Changing... Clothes
201352.desc: It's okay, Janus. You're just getting dressed, so do it like usual, and everything will be fine... Hwuh? Commander? S-sorry! I'm the one who told you to keep your eyes closed, so why did I go and talk to you?!

201361.name: The Devil Wears Knee-Highs
201361.desc: Morning, Commander. Looks like our desks are right next to each other~ Whee~☆ Hmm? What's up? Is there something on my skirt? Teehee~♪

202010.name: Leander
202010.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Leander, Hull Number 75!

202019.name: Leander (Retrofit)
202019.desc: Everything as you wish, Commander. Oh? Yes, I'm Leander!

202020.name: Achilles
202020.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Achilles, Hull Number 70!

202029.name: Achilles (Retrofit)
202029.desc: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆

202030.name: Ajax
202030.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Ajax, Hull Number 22!

202031.name: Party Queen
202031.desc: Ahaha, that slovenly expression on your face proves I made the right wardrobe choice♪ Now then, Commander, can I offer you some wine?

202032.name: Valentine's Reward?
202032.desc: I have some special chocolate right here, just~ for~ you. Hehe, if you want it so badly... then come and get it~

202039.name: Ajax (Retrofit)
202039.desc: I'll allow you to lick my feet since I'm in such a good mood today. What? I can't believe you'd turn down such a great opportunity!

202041.name: Anxious Bisque Doll
202041.desc: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!

202071.name: New Year's Little Knight
202071.desc: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~

202072.name: Afternoon Impromptu
202072.desc: Good day, Comm—Err, I guess it's "Master?" Ugh, I do prefer calling you Commander though... Anyway, I've been practicing the violin to help create better atmosphere around the shop. Did you come here because you were captivated by the sound of my music?

202078.name: A Dazzling Departure
202078.desc: The Royal Knight, Southampton, makes her grand entrance in glorious wedding garb~! Oh, Commander, you look a bit on edge. Here, c'mere for a second~ Ehehe. *rub rub* Well? Feeling a bit less stiff?

202081.name: Cloak and Dagger
202081.desc: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

202082.name: A Moment's Respite
202082.desc: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

202083.name: Black Crow's Finery
202083.desc: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

202084.name: Bulletborne
202084.desc: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

202091.name: Midnight Devil in White
202091.desc: Master, it's time for your injection! Hmm... Nowhere to be seen, eh... Then I guess I'll keep the sickbed warm until Master comes ba– Eep! M-M-Master?!

202101.name: Brilliance in Purple
202101.desc: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.

202110.name: Edinburgh
202110.desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!

202111.name: The Library Fairy
202111.desc: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

202112.name: Candy Maid
202112.desc: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

202120.name: Belfast
202120.desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Belfast, Hull number C35!

202121.name: Iridescent Rosa
202121.desc: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?

202122.name: Serene Steel
202122.desc: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.

202123.name: The Noble Attendant
202123.desc: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.

202124.name: Shopping with the Head Maid
202124.desc: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."

202125.name: Piping-Hot Perfection
202125.desc: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?

202126.name: Folded Fascination
202126.desc: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?

202128.name: The Pledge of Claddagh
202128.desc: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.

202130.name: Arethusa
202130.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Arethusa, Hull Number 26!

202140.name: Galatea
202140.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!

202150.name: Aurora
202150.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12

202151.name: The Tale of Spring
202151.desc: I've been preparing for this day for quite some time... Commander, would you like to hear the book I wrote for you?

202152.name: Dawn's Paean
202152.desc: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.

202153.name: Heritage of Yu City
202153.desc: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?

202158.name: Garb of Eternal Prosperity
202158.desc: Commander, please relax and take a seat. This is a special place for just the two of us... Just kidding, did I get your heart racing just now? Ehehe~

202161.name: Trendy and Vogue?
202161.desc: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~

202171.name: Dark Bolt
202171.desc: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?

202172.name: Highway Star
202172.desc: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?

202191.name: Hibiscus Garments
202191.desc: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.

202199.name: Newcastle (Retrofit)
202199.desc: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.

202201.name: White Rose
202201.desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

202202.name: Scorching-Hot Seirios
202202.desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?

202203.name: Azure Horizons
202203.desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?

202211.name: Eastern Grace
202211.desc: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...

202219.name: Curacoa (Retrofit)
202219.desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.

202221.name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery
202221.desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

202229.name: Curlew (Retrofit)
202229.desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.

202230.name: Swiftsure
202230.desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.

202231.name: Study Hall Cyclamen
202231.desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.

202232.name: Beauty of White Jade
202232.desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...

202233.name: Midsummer Special Service
202233.desc: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?

202240.name: Black Prince
202240.desc: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?

202241.name: White Princess
202241.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

202242.name: Fair Maid Spring
202242.desc: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?

202243.name: Pop the Cork
202243.desc: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!

202244.name: Addled Attendant?
202244.desc: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

202250.name: Sheffield μ
202250.desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.

202261.name: A Maid in Class
202261.desc: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

202271.name: Pure White Angel
202271.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...

202272.name: Pure White Holiday
202272.desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.

202273.name: Graceful Afternoon Tea
202273.desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.

202274.name: Pristine Herbalist
202274.desc: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~

202280.name: Dido µ
202280.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!

202291.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir
202291.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?

202292.name: Salty Maid
202292.desc: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.

202301.name: Red Chamber of Healing
202301.desc: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~

202302.name: Brilliant Belle
202302.desc: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!

202303.name: Prim Sea Breeze
202303.desc: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪

202311.name: Armed to Clean
202311.desc: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.

202331.name: Femme Fatale Fresher
202331.desc: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪

203010.name: London
203010.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!

203018.name: Platinum Ceremony
203018.desc: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?

203019.name: London (Retrofit)
